{"type":"message","id":"594e5bc2","parentId":"23a86c11","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:33:29.426Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-17 12:31:16 GMT+8] Gateway restart restart ok (gateway.restart)\nSystem: 添加 scnet 模型提供商和 MiniMax-M2.5 模型后重启\nSystem: Run: openclaw doctor --non-interactive\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 12:33 GMT+8] 请学习一个网页语音视频转文字的skill"}],"timestamp":1773722009411}}
{"type":"message","id":"e0b99333","parentId":"594e5bc2","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:33:35.217Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我学习一个网页语音视频转文字的skill。这可能涉及到语音识别/转文字的功能。让我看看有什么相关的skill可用。\n\n从available_skills中我看到有一个：\n- miaoda-speech-to-text: 语音转文字相关的skill\n\n让我先读取这个skill看看。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你找找语音视频转文字相关的skill。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k592j3loz25r_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-speech-to-text/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":18012,"output":115,"cacheRead":30205,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48332,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773722009418}}
{"type":"message","id":"89ca0826","parentId":"e0b99333","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:33:35.250Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_k592j3loz25r_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: miaoda-speech-to-text\ndescription: \"Use when user needs to convert audio or voice recordings to text. Provides necessary command usage instructions for converting audio to text. Supports multiple languages. 触发词：语音转文字, 音频转文字, 语音识别, speech to text, STT, 转录, 听写, 会议记录转文字, 录音转文字, transcribe, 音频识别, voice to text, 语音转换\"\n---\n\n# Speech to Text\n\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli speech-to-text` 将音频文件转换为文字。\n\n## Quick Reference\n\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\n|------|------|------|--------|\n| `--file` | 音频文件路径 | 是 | - |\n| `--lang` | 语言代码 | 否 | zh |\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\n\n## 支持的语言\n\n| 代码 | 语言 | 代码 | 语言 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| `zh` | 中文（默认） | `fr` | 法语 |\n| `en` | 英语 | `es` | 西班牙语 |\n| `ja` | 日语 | `pt` | 葡萄牙语 |\n| `ko` | 韩语 | `id` | 印尼语 |\n| `ru` | 俄语 | `ms` | 马来语 |\n\n## 使用示例\n\n```bash\n# 中文音频转文字（默认语言）\nmiaoda-studio-cli speech-to-text --file meeting.mp3\n\n# 英文音频转文字\nmiaoda-studio-cli speech-to-text --file interview.wav --lang en\n\n# 获取 JSON 格式输出\nmiaoda-studio-cli speech-to-text --file recording.mp3 --lang zh --output json\n```\n\n## 使用场景\n\n| 场景 | 用法 |\n|------|------|\n| 会议录音转文字 | `miaoda-studio-cli speech-to-text --file meeting.mp3 --lang zh` |\n| 外语音频转录 | `miaoda-studio-cli speech-to-text --file audio.mp3 --lang en` |\n| 转录后搜索补充资料 | 先 `miaoda-studio-cli speech-to-text` 转录，再用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 搜索关键内容（见 miaoda-web-search skill） |\n\n## Common Mistakes\n\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\n|------|----------|\n| 音频文件超过 10 分钟 | 拆分为更短的音频片段后分别转录 |\n| 音频语言与 `--lang` 不匹配 | 确认音频实际语言，指定正确的语言代码 |\n| 混合语言音频用单一语言代码 | 以主要语言为准，或按语言段落拆分音频 |\n| 需要后续处理但未加 `--output json` | 需要程序处理转录结果时加 `--output json` |\n| 命令失败后不检查 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查文件路径和格式后重试 |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773722015242}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd77c531","parentId":"89ca0826","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:33:41.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个语音转文字的skill，通过 miaoda-studio-cli 工具。用户说的是\"网页语音视频转文字\"，这个skill是针对本地音频文件的。\n\n让我告诉用户这个skill的信息，看看是否符合他的需求。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！这是 **miaoda-speech-to-text** skill 🎤\n\n**功能：** 将音频/语音转换为文字（支持多种语言）\n\n**常用命令：**\n```bash\n# 中文音频转文字\nmiaoda-studio-cli speech-to-text --file 你的音频文件.mp3\n\n# 英文音频转文字  \nmiaoda-studio-cli speech-to-text --file audio.wav --lang en\n```\n\n**支持格式：** MP3、WAV、AAC 等常见音频格式\n\n不过这个skill是针对**本地音频文件**的。如果你是要从**网页在线**提取语音（比如YouTube视频、网页音频），可能需要先用 miaoda-web-fetch 抓取网页内容，或者告诉我具体场景，我可以帮你看看怎么实现 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":836,"output":196,"cacheRead":48125,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49157,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773722015248}}
{"type":"message","id":"4546d0a1","parentId":"dd77c531","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:34:57.259Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 12:34 GMT+8] https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fRS4BPEfK?spm_id_from=333.788.videopod.sections&vd_source=0445c985fdfd2570ddd86ce8cd2062d7&p=3提取并整理这个网页视频里的语音转换成讲稿"}],"timestamp":1773722097254}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4eaedb6","parentId":"4546d0a1","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:35:06.047Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要从一个B站视频中提取语音并转换成文字讲稿。我需要：\n\n1. 首先使用浏览器访问这个网页，获取视频内容\n2. 提取视频中的语音/字幕\n3. 转换成文字讲稿\n\nB站视频的语音提取可能有几种方式：\n1. 如果有字幕，可以直接提取字幕\n2. 使用语音转文字工具\n\n让我先尝试用浏览器打开这个页面，看看能否获取到字幕或者视频信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qof1jjq3fw63_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"open","url":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fRS4BPEfK?p=3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":1052,"output":149,"cacheRead":48125,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49326,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773722097256}}
